gr.interamerican.bo2.arch.records
Interface ModifiableIndexedFieldsRecord<T>

Type Parameters:
T -
All Superinterfaces:
IndexedFieldsRecord<T>, Record
public interface ModifiableIndexedFieldsRecord<T>
extends IndexedFieldsRecord<T>

A record that can have its values changed. The record offers setter methods for modification of its field's values.
